br> <br> <i>Thrilling Tremors</i> can only be triggered once every <span style=\"color:#FFD700; font-weight: bold\">100</span>/<span style=\"color:#7CFC00; font-weight: bold\">80</span>/<span style=\"color:#CF9FFF; font-weight: bold\">60</span> <span style=\"color:#FFA500; font-weight: bold\">seconds.</span>","url":"https://deadbydaylight.fandom.com/wiki/Thrilling_Tremors","img_url":"images/perks/iconPerks_thrillingTremors.png"}]}